cs.IT, cs.DS, cs.AR, cs.SY, cs.ET

This paper deals with modulation codes for flash memory storage systems, which involves information theory (cs.IT) and data structures (cs.DS). The use of load-balancing theory suggests that it could also fall under the categories of computer architecture (cs.AR) and control systems (cs.SY). Additionally, the paper proposes a self-randomized modulation code, which could be related to error-correcting codes (cs.ET).
